  "detailed_description": "<h1>UPDATE 2.0</h1><p>Update 2.0 is finally out and it introduces many changes, fixes and overall improvements the community has been asking for!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Discover various levels of danger while trying to escape the eerily familiar backrooms based on popular creepypasta lore.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New and Unique Levels</h2>Traverse through 20+ unique levels based on the Backrooms lore. Regular content updates will add even more levels. Each level features a different way to escape, with various dangers along the way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scary Entities</h2>In The Backrooms Deluxe, there are many entities blocking your way of finally exiting the backrooms. Each of the entities has its own appearance and mechanics<br><br>Join the official Discord Server for updates about it! <i>(updates will still be posted on Steam but the discord server has sneak peeks about it)</i>",
  "about_the_game": "Discover various levels of danger while trying to escape the eerily familiar backrooms based on popular creepypasta lore.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New and Unique Levels</h2>Traverse through 20+ unique levels based on the Backrooms lore. Regular content updates will add even more levels. Each level features a different way to escape, with various dangers along the way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scary Entities</h2>In The Backrooms Deluxe, there are many entities blocking your way of finally exiting the backrooms. Each of the entities has its own appearance and mechanics<br><br>Join the official Discord Server for updates about it! <i>(updates will still be posted on Steam but the discord server has sneak peeks about it)</i>",
